                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321129-42-off245 t18321129-42-cd246"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 5s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18321129-42-victim478" type="victimName">
